---
By: Marcus Aurelius
Source:
  ID: 57c5499b-c3b2-4b09-92a9-a6e977a32050
  Locus:
    Page: 76
    Verse: 13
Tags:
  - Death
---
Death is a release from the impressions of the senses, and from the desires
that make us their puppets, and from the vagaries of the mind, and from the
hard service of the flesh.
